data.description: Solid brick Jumbo 2-Flat with an unfinished basement. Each unit has a large living room and dining room, as well as an eat-in kitchen. The 1st floor boasts 3bd/1ba (vacant), while the 2nd floor has 5bd/1ba ($1,500 MTM). The property has separate utilities, a newer gas furnace, separate water heaters, and washer and dryer hookup for both units. Additionally, storage is available for both units, and a fenced yard.  This jumbo 2-flat could be a great investment opportunity for someone looking to rent out both units or live in one unit and rent out the other.  Basement is 7 foot high opportunity for an ADU.  Seller has an FHA assumable loan of 265k for 2.7% interest rate.
